    "row": 24,
    "rowsha": "co9p+mpyRovUCF96VIRAb+t95qzgOawBzpGHi/KhiMQ=",
    "originContent": "Most database work runs locally in the browser through WebAssembly and a web",
    "translatedContent": "可选功能如 URL 加载、CORS 代理回退、Google 字体和 Gemini 驱动的查询生成使用网络请求。"
